---
// 高颜值 404
---

<html lang="zh" class="overflow-hidden">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no" />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/logo.svg" />
  <title>页面不见了 - Novatra AI</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <script>
    if (localStorage.theme === 'dark' || (!('theme' in localStorage) && window.matchMedia('(prefers-color-scheme: dark)').matches)) {
      document.documentElement.classList.add('dark');
    }
  </script>
</head>
<body class="flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen bg-stone-50 dark:bg-stone-950 text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100">
  <div class="text-center space-y-6">
    <img src="/logo.svg" alt="Logo" class="h-16 mx-auto" />
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold">404</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-400">页面好像迷路了</p>
    <p class="text-sm text-stone-500 dark:text-stone-500">别担心，技术的探索总是伴随着未知。</p>
    <a href="/" class="inline-block mt-4 px-6 py-2 bg-stone-900 dark:bg-stone-100 text-white dark:text-stone-900 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:opacity-90 transition">
      返回首页
    </a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>